question: Give me all world heritage sites designated within the past two years.

```
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

SELECT ?site WHERE {
  ?site a dbo:WorldHeritageSite .
  ?site dbo:yearOfInscription ?year .
  FILTER (?year >= "2014"^^xsd:gYear)
}
```

Please note that this query assumes that the current year is 2016, and it will return all World Heritage Sites that were designated in 2014 or later.

question: Show me all songs from Bruce Springsteen released between 1980 and 1990.
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

  FILTER (?releaseDate >= "1980-01-01"^^xsd:date && ?releaseDate <= "1990-12-31"^^xsd:date)
}

question: In which countries do people speak Japanese?
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?country 
WHERE {
  ?country dbo:officialLanguage ?language .
  ?language rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER (lang(?label) = 'en' && ?label = 'Japanese') .
}

question: Which of Tim Burton's films had the highest budget?
sparql:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>

SELECT ?film ?budget
WHERE {
  ?film dbo:director ?director .
  ?director foaf:name "Tim Burton" .
  ?film dbo:budget ?budget .
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
